{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "e7f1a80e-e17e-4033-807f-53930842d436", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/e7f1a80e-e17e-4033-807f-53930842d436@1.pkg/1772597657108/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597657861", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/e7f1a80e-e17e-4033-807f-53930842d436@1.pkg/1772597657108/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597657861"}, "identifier": "e7f1a80e-e17e-4033-807f-53930842d436", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>本题考查对法律的认识和理解。</p>\n\n<p>A 错误，题干主要强调的是民营经济促进法这一法律的实施意义，未涉及德治相关内容，与法治与德治相结合的治国理念关联不大。​</p>\n\n<p>B 错误，“彻底解决民营经济发展中的所有问题” 说法过于绝对，一部法律的实施能为民营经济发展提供法治保障，但无法解决所有问题，民营经济发展还受多种因素影响。​</p>\n\n<p>C 错误，调整平等主体间的人身和财产关系是民法典的主要作用，并非民营经济促进法的功能。​</p>\n\n<p>D 正确，民营经济促进法作为专门规范民营经济发展的基础性法律，其实施能够为民营经济发展营造稳定、公平的法治化营商环境，保障民营经济依法平等使用生产要素、公平参与市场竞争等，符合题意。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>（改编）2025年5月起施行的民营经济促进法，是我国第一部专门关于民营经济发展的基础性法律，这将填补我国民营经济领域立法的空白。该法律的实施有利于（ &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "title": "（改编）2025年5月起施行的民营经济促进法，是我国第一部专门关于民营经济发展的基础性法律，这将填补我国民营经济领域立法的空白。该法律的实施有利于（     ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["D"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/e7f1a80e-e17e-4033-807f-53930842d436@1.pkg/item.json?v=1755143060276", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>坚持法治与德治相结合的治国理念</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>彻底解决民营经济发展中所有问题</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>调整平等主体间的人身和财产关系</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p>营造稳定、公平的法治化营商环境</p>\n"}], "prompt": "<p>（改编）2025年5月起施行的民营经济促进法，是我国第一部专门关于民营经济发展的基础性法律，这将填补我国民营经济领域立法的空白。该法律的实施有利于（ &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "5136342961", "5036342749", "$RE0200", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bebf7c-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "5136342961", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bebf7c-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "e7f1a80e-e17e-4033-807f-53930842d436", "global_title": {"zh-CN": "（改编）2025年5月起施行的民营经济促进法，是我国第一部专门关于民营经济发展的基础性法律，这将填补我国民营经济领域立法的空白。该法律的实施有利于（     ）"}, "global_description": {"zh-CN": "<p>（改编）2025年5月起施行的民营经济促